{"tid":2123094,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃店食評］西營盤Pop street","createTime":"2020-07-24T11:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T01:53:05.000Z","uid":354871,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ac79e0c2fab32eb50daf68d3a0c09f1651d6f3","tid":2123094,"uid":354871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"新手第一次打食評 今次多字少圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />望多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排疫情下得閒咗 於是出去試咗幾間黃店<br />\n<br />\n今次去第三街嘅Pop Street 主打fushion西餐<br />\n<br />\n一望到舖面 就見到連儂牆黐咗D memo紙<br />\n<br />\n入去有個open kitchen連minibar<br />\n<br />\n成間餐廳主要行工業風 有隻用粉筆畫嘅連豬係牆上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐低咗侍應就講低Pasta of the day同是日涼茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rBuoP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rBuoP6.png&h=7ea108d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前菜今次係涼拌蕃茄 之前係炸餃子 蕃茄比較fresh 不過煮得唔夠耐 偏硬同冇去到皮<br />\n<br />\n而主菜 就揀左pasta of the day:茄汁豬柳扁意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果食辣periperi chicken 都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個冇圖 整體上幾好 茄汁唔係一味茄膏底 意粉冇煮過龍 豬柳正常texture 完全冇用鬆肉粉醃果種感覺 不過同時唔太入味 <br />\n最後飲品有得揀Lemonade 好正<br />\n埋單$70 冇加一<br />\n<br />\n個價位喺同區西餐算抵食 味道唔太浮誇 貼地D<br />\n好似晚餐都同一價錢<br />\n過咗限眾令 大家可以試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188f5e13a73d8ade96c39c03165774f5f4051de0","tid":2123094,"uid":251207,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"少圖都唔係問題 起碼都影個主菜丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a724024bd9078b7f50feb0ac9ac3a0ecc587db8","tid":2123094,"uid":342510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"188f5